text:
Passed by the mall, and spouse decided to weigh himself at the weighing machine at the malls entrance.
After dropping in 20 cents, my spouse proceeded to weigh himself. To our surprise, the machine doesn't reflect the accurate weight and HE IS UNDERWEIGHT now which obviously he is not.

Hence, this review is merely to remind others not to waste your money on this weighing scale parked at the Sultan plaza entrance.
Nothing much going on in this shopping mall except for some eateries and massage parlours at level 1.
Needs a revamp but like since 80s however most people who come here already know that n they dun mind I am sure. Mostly for office and small business
The Otoko cafe at Sultan plaza offer very affordable Japanese food and as good taste compare to those from a Japanese restaurants. A must try!
